  $ pavuk -nostore_index 
          -ftpdir -ftplist
          -cdir /home/maierha/tmp  
          ftp://maierha:34Thaele@localhost/impos-3.0/impos


  - nostore_index	Does not create html index files
  - ftpdir		Get all recursive
  - ftplist             This ignores symbolic links
  - cdir                Where to place the directory

  - created directory is  <prot>/<host>_<port>/
